title: Maya Millete Person of Interest NAMED Plus Niqui McCown Update
author: LordanARTS
comment: The question remains: If Larry is so innocent in the disappearance of Maya, why wouldn't he be happy for his children to continue the relationship with Maya's side of the family? The fact that he is not allowing them to visit speaks volumes about his character and involvement. He is doing this to punish Maya's family because he knows they have his number.

‘Despite all i’ve endured…’
Malignant Narcissist Sociopath.
Maya's family, especially her sister & brother-in-law are absolute WARRIORS. I hope that they get the justice that they are seeking for Maya.
So happy to see these two ladies’ pictures with UPDATE beside them. They deserve justice!

People are asking the wrong questions regarding May's case. Stop focusing on how many guns there were, for God's sake. First, kids have no business with access to ANY guns, whether one or twenty. The guy is shady as hell. Definitely involved.
